OL,3,CTributes paid to 'warm and gentle'
OL,4,Cengineer following fatal crash
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died in a
OL,7,Fcollision have paid tribute to him as
OL,8,Fa "warm, friendly, and gentle" person.
OL,10,FAlex James Edwards, aged 22, from
OL,11,FMontgomeryshire, was involved in a
OL,12,Fcollision near the Llandrinio bridge,
OL,13,FPowys, at 7.20am on Monday, 16
OL,14,FSeptember.
OL,16,FPolice are investigating the incident
OL,17,Fand are appealing to anyone who may
OL,18,Fhave been travelling along the B4393
OL,19,Fnear the bridge at the time, to come
OL,20,Fforward.
