OL,4,Cengineer following fatal crash
OL,6,FThe collision involved a white
OL,7,FVauxhall van and a black Kawasaki
OL,8,Fmotorcycle. The motorcyclist died at
OL,9,Fthe scene and has now been named as
OL,10,FAlex James Edwards.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Alex's family said:
OL,13,F"Living in Guilsfield, Alex worked as
OL,14,Fan apprentice engineer at Technocover
OL,15,FLtd in Welshpool.
OL,17,F"With his warm, friendly and gentle
OL,18,Fnature, Alex left a lasting impression
OL,19,Fon those who got to know him.
