OL,6,F"Alex will be missed beyond words by
OL,7,Fthose who loved him so dearly,
OL,8,Fespecially his mum Bryony, dad Steve,
OL,9,Fhis sister Katherine, his girlfriend
OL,10,FMacy, his family and friends."
OL,12,FInvestigating officers have also
OL,13,Fappealed to speak to motorists who
OL,14,Fwere in the area at that time who may
OL,15,Fhave dash cam in their vehicles.
